<template>
    <svg enable-background="new 0 0 32 32" :height="IconSize" id="Layer_1" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 32 32" :width="IconSize"
        xml:space="preserve" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
        <g>
            <g>
                <path
                    d="M1.911,16.179c-1.084,0.568-1.039,1.4,0.098,1.852l3.364,1.331c1.137,0.449,2.856,0.204,3.821-0.55    L23.806,7.289c0.961-0.757,1.064-0.645,0.229,0.249L12.483,19.902c-0.837,0.892-0.59,1.984,0.55,2.425l0.394,0.154    c1.14,0.44,3,1.182,4.132,1.642l3.732,1.521c1.133,0.46,2.06,0.842,2.062,0.849c0.001,0.007,0.006,0.028,0.012,0.03    s0.273-0.962,0.594-2.141l5.688-20.908c0.321-1.18-0.302-1.681-1.385-1.113L1.911,16.179z"
                    :fill="IconColor" />
            </g>
            <g>
                <path
                    d="M11.146,29.864c-0.067,0.199,2.301-3.429,2.301-3.429c0.669-1.022,0.29-2.241-0.842-2.703l-2.582-1.058    c-1.132-0.463-1.674,0.08-1.205,1.212C8.818,23.887,11.214,29.66,11.146,29.864z"
                    :fill="IconColor" />
            </g>
        </g>
    </svg>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: 'ShareIcon',
        props:{
            size:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            },
            color:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            }
        },
        data(){
            return{
                IconSize:null,
                IconColor:null,
            }
        },
        mounted(){
            this.getSize();
            this.getColor();
        },
        methods:{
            getSize(){
                if (this.$props.size){
                    this.IconSize=this.$props.size
                    return
                }
                this.IconSize="30px"
                return
            },
            getColor(){
                if (this.$props.color){
                    this.IconColor=this.$props.color
                    return
                }
                this.IconColor="#000000"
                return
            },
            AddPost(){
                this.$emit("AddPost")
            }
        },
    }
</script>
